Package: FAScore
Type: Package
Title: Measure the dynamism and functionality of alternative splicing events
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Li Chen
Maintainer: Li Chen <chenli5679@163.com>
Description: Calculate dynamic scores of genes or AS and functional AS scores in a biology process to measure the dynamism and 
    functionality of a alternative splicing event. The functional AS were identified by random forest predicted model using 
    the dynamism of expression and structure of transcripts. 
